#: resources/locales/en/methodology.md:93
msgid "Uncertainty"
msgstr ""

#: resources/locales/en/methodology.md:95
msgid "Uncertainty of the input data"
msgstr ""

#: resources/locales/en/methodology.md:97
msgid ""
"Spatial data from the German census: As this is official data from administrative sources, we assume very low "
"(negligible) uncertainty"
msgstr ""

#: resources/locales/en/methodology.md:98
